{"lemma":"نَكِيرٌ","slug":"نَكِيرٌ","root":"ن.ك.ر","root_slug":"ن-ك-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ك-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نَكِير","root":"نكر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40528"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%83%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40528","headword_ar":"نَكِيرٌ","root":"nkr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inokaArN","text_ar":"اـِنْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the sense of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Denial"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) It is said in the Kur, xlii. 46."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"famaA lakumo mino nakiyrK","text_ar":"فَمَا لَكُمْ مِنْ نَكِيرٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And there shall be for you no"},{"kind":"text","text":"[power of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"denial"},{"kind":"text","text":"of your sins. (Bd, Jel.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$utima","text_ar":"شُتِمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN famaA kaAna Einodahu nakiyrN","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ فَمَا كَانَ عِنْدَهُ نَكِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was reviled and he had no denial to make"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  [Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inokaArN","text_ar":"اـِنْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Disapproval,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manifestation thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"See what here follows.] ―         -b3-  Also,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inokaArN","text_ar":"اـِنْكَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"changing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a thing]: (T, Msb, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"changing what is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munokar","text_ar":"مُنْكَر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disapproved"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) a simple subst. (T, TA.) The words of the Kur, [xxii. 43 and lxvii. 18,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fakayofa kaAna nakiyri","text_ar":"فَكَيْفَ كَانَ نَكِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are explained as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And how was my changing"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of their condition]! (TA:) or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and how was my manifestation of disapproval of their conduct,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_inokaAriY Ealayohimo","text_ar":"اـِنْكَارِى عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) by changing favour into trial, and life into destruction, and a flourishing condition into a state of ruin! (Bd, xxii. 43.) In [some of] the copies of the K, it is said that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakiyrapN","text_ar":"نَكِيرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but in a MS. copy I find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nakiyrN","text_ar":"نَكِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so in the CK] is a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tanak~urN","text_ar":"تَنَكُّرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as signifying the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"changing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altering, oneself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"itself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becoming changed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"altered; from a state which please one to a state which one dislikes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"but a different statement is found in the T: [see above.] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nkyrp","text_ar":"نكيرة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is not mentioned by any authority. (TA.)       -A2-  A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong"},{"kind":"text","text":"fortress. (Sgh, K.) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nukorN","text_ar":"نُكْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"munokarN","text_ar":"مُنْكَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T","Msb","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}